compiz: compiz (Compiz Fusion OpenGL Window Manager)
compiz:
compiz: Compiz is a compositing window manager that uses 3D graphics 
compiz: acceleration via OpenGL. It provides various new graphical effects 
compiz: and features on any desktop environment, including GNOME. It seeks to 
compiz: provide an easy and fun-to-use windowing environment, allowing use of 
compiz: the graphics hardware to provide impressive effects, amazing speed 
compiz: and unrivalled usefulness.
